Source:http://news.mit.edu/2017/identifying-optimal-product-prices-0918

AGENT:online retailers

GOAL:to increase revenue in online shopping

DATA:

Methods:matcheing a product with others with similar charecteristics a relationship between demand and price is predicted with a machine learning algoritm secondly changing the price based on pricing curves for it and then a new curve is applied to help optimize priceing across many products and time periods

Results: the methods increased the revenue by about 21 percent in some cases so average revenue was 116%

